### 5. REFUNDS — lib/features/refunds/data/services/refund_api_service.dart
### =====================================================================

### 5.1 List Refunds (default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/refunds?page=1&per_page=15&sort_by=created_at&sort_direction=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: {{accept}}

### 5.2 List Refunds — full filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/refunds?page=1&per_page=15&search=REF&store_id={{storeId}}&user_id=1&customer_id={{customerId}}&date_from=2026-01-01&date_to=2026-12-31&status=completed&refund_method=cash&min_amount=1000&max_amount=500000&sort_by=created_at&sort_direction=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: {{accept}}

### 5.3 List Refunds — by transaction_id
GET {{baseUrl}}/refunds?transaction_id={{transactionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: {{accept}}

### 5.4 Get Refund Detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/refunds/{{refundId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: {{accept}}

### 5.5 Create Refund (cash)
POST {{baseUrl}}/refunds
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{accept}}

{
  "transaction_id": {{transactionId}},
  "store_id": {{storeId}},
  "refund_method": "cash",
  "cash_refund_amount": 25000,
  "transfer_refund_amount": 0,
  "status": "completed",
  "notes": "Refund test dari REST Client",
  "refund_date": "2026-05-04T10:30:00.000Z",
  "details": [
    {
      "transaction_detail_id": 1,
      "quantity_refunded": 1
    }
  ]
}

### 5.6 Create Refund (split — cash + transfer)
POST {{baseUrl}}/refunds
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{accept}}

{
  "transaction_id": {{transactionId}},
  "store_id": {{storeId}},
  "refund_method": "mixed",
  "cash_refund_amount": 15000,
  "transfer_refund_amount": 10000,
  "status": "completed",
  "refund_date": "2026-05-04T10:30:00.000Z",
  "details": [
    {
      "transaction_detail_id": 1,
      "quantity_refunded": 1
    }
  ]
}


### =====================================================================
### 6. CASH FLOWS — lib/features/cash_flows/data/services/cash_flow_api_service.dart
### =====================================================================

### 6.1 List Cash Flows
GET {{baseUrl}}/cash-flows?store_id={{storeId}}&page=1&per_page=15
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: {{accept}}

### 6.2 List Cash Flows — filter type, category, date
GET {{baseUrl}}/cash-flows?store_id={{storeId}}&type=in&category=penjualan&date_from=2026-01-01&date_to=2026-12-31&page=1&per_page=15
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: {{accept}}

### 6.3 Create Cash Flow — IN (multipart/form-data)
### Catatan: app menggunakan multipart, bukan JSON.
POST {{baseUrl}}/cash-flows
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: {{accept}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----SunPosBoundary

------SunPosBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="store_id"

{{storeId}}
------SunPosBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Penjualan tunai
------SunPosBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Setoran kasir akhir hari
------SunPosBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="amount"

500000
------SunPosBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="type"

in
------SunPosBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

penjualan
------SunPosBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="transaction_date"

2026-05-04
------SunPosBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="notes"

Test dari REST Client
------SunPosBoundary--

### 6.4 Create Cash Flow — OUT (multipart/form-data)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cash-flows
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: {{accept}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----SunPosBoundary

------SunPosBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="store_id"

{{storeId}}
------SunPosBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Beli ATK
------SunPosBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Pembelian alat tulis kantor
------SunPosBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="amount"

75000
------SunPosBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="type"

out
------SunPosBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

operasional
------SunPosBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="transaction_date"

2026-05-04
------SunPosBoundary--


