### =====================================================================
### 8. CONTOH CHAINING — login → pakai token-nya otomatis
### =====================================================================
### Setelah jalankan request di bawah, request berikutnya bisa pakai
### {{loginChain.response.body.data.token}} tanpa perlu copy-paste.

### 8.1 Login (chained)
# @name loginChain
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{accept}}

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 8.2 Auto pakai token dari response 8.1
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{loginChain.response.body.data.token}}
Accept: {{accept}}
